CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 19, 1956, pg. 19, reads: "Mother's Helper...in this case is Shelia Richbourg, who enjoys going shopping with her mother, Mrs. V. M. Richbourg of Pittsburgh. They do most of their shopping in a super market. - 'Teenie' Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Mrs. V. M. Richbourg and her daughter Shelia, with full shopping cart, in grocery store offering Top Value Stamps
